summary: This is a multi-line chart with 2 lines representing Full-line stores, and Specialty stores.
The line for Full-line stores has the highest values across Year with a mean value of 724.86,
and it peaked at 2011 with a value of 867.0.
Specialty stores mostly had the least y-axis name with a mean value of 220.71,
which peaked at 2011 with a value of 1338.0.
Specialty stores reported the highest y-axis name  about 1338.0 in Year 2011
Specialty stores reported the lowest y-axis name  about 23.0 in Year 2017
Overall Specialty stores is rapidly decreasing, Full-line stores is gradually decreasing,  throughout the Year
The difference of y_axis name between Full-line stores and Specialty stores is greater at Year 2017 compared to the Year 2011.
The greatest difference of y_axis name between Full-line stores and Specialty stores occurs at Year 2012 and the smallest difference occurs at 2011.
